imes.com/2016/07/26/nyregion/new-yorks-first-zoning-resolution-which-brought-order-to-a-chaotic-building-boom-turns-100.html|work=[[The New York Times]]|accessdate=July 13, 2019|page=A21|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190711221354/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/26/nyregion/new-yorks-first-zoning-resolution-which-brought-order-to-a-chaotic-building-boom-turns-100.html|archivedate=July 11, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"english_2018\">{{cite web|author=English, Jonathan|date=April 16, 2018|url=https://www.citylab.com/transportation/2018/04/why-new-york-city-stopped-building-subways/557567/|title=Why New York City Stopped Building Subways|website=CityLab|accessdate=July 13, 2019|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630033140/https://www.citylab.com/transportation/2018/04/why-new-york-city-stopped-building-subways/557567/|archivedate=June 30, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"flowers_2011\">{{cite book|author=Flowers, Benjamin|year=2011|title=Skyscraper: The Politics and Power of Building New York City in the Twentieth Century|publisher=University of Pennsylvania Press|isbn=9780812202601}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"goldberger_1990\">{{cite news|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C0CE5D71730F936A25757C0A966958260|title=Architecture View; A Commission that has Itself Become a Landmark|accessdate=March 17, 2008|date=April 15, 1990|author=[[Paul Goldberger|Goldberger, Paul]]|newspaper=[[The New York Times]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"gray_1994-02-20\">{{cite web|author=Gray, Christopher|date=February 20, 1994|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1994/02/20/realestate/streetscapes-the-american-radiator-building-a-1924-precursor-of-art-deco.html|title=Streetscapes/The American Radiator Building; A 1924 Precursor of Art Deco|work=[[The New York Times]]|accessdate=July 27, 2019|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180624100315/https://www.nytimes.com/1994/02/20/realestate/streetscapes-the-american-radiator-building-a-